<span class="typ-heading">= Animation</span>

<span class="typ-heading">== Simple Animation</span>

We can use <span class="typ-raw">`#pause`</span> to <span class="typ-pol">#</span><span class="typ-pol">pause</span> display something later.

<span class="typ-pol">#</span><span class="typ-pol">pause</span>

Just like this.

<span class="typ-pol">#</span><span class="typ-pol">meanwhile</span>

Meanwhile, <span class="typ-pol">#</span><span class="typ-pol">pause</span> we can also use <span class="typ-raw">`#meanwhile`</span> to <span class="typ-pol">#</span><span class="typ-pol">pause</span> display other content synchronously.

<span class="typ-func">#</span><span class="typ-func">speaker-note</span><span class="typ-punct">[</span>
  <span class="typ-marker">+</span> This is a speaker note.
  <span class="typ-marker">+</span> You won't see it unless you use <span class="typ-raw">`config-common(show-notes-on-second-screen: right)`</span>
<span class="typ-punct">]</span>


<span class="typ-heading">== Complex Animation</span>

At subslide <span class="typ-func">#</span><span class="typ-func">touying-fn-wrapper</span><span class="typ-punct">(</span><span class="typ-punct">(</span>self<span class="typ-punct">:</span> <span class="typ-key">none</span><span class="typ-punct">)</span> <span class="typ-op">=&gt;</span> <span class="typ-func">str</span><span class="typ-punct">(</span>self<span class="typ-punct">.</span>subslide<span class="typ-punct">)</span><span class="typ-punct">)</span>, we can

use <span class="typ-func">#</span><span class="typ-func">uncover</span><span class="typ-punct">(</span><span class="typ-str">"2-"</span><span class="typ-punct">)</span><span class="typ-punct">[</span><span class="typ-raw">`#uncover`</span> function<span class="typ-punct">]</span> for reserving space,

use <span class="typ-func">#</span><span class="typ-func">only</span><span class="typ-punct">(</span><span class="typ-str">"2-"</span><span class="typ-punct">)</span><span class="typ-punct">[</span><span class="typ-raw">`#only`</span> function<span class="typ-punct">]</span> for not reserving space,

<span class="typ-func">#</span><span class="typ-func">alternatives</span><span class="typ-punct">[</span>call <span class="typ-raw">`#only`</span> multiple times <span class="typ-escape">\u{2717}</span><span class="typ-punct">]</span><span class="typ-punct">[</span>use <span class="typ-raw">`#alternatives`</span> function <span class="typ-pol">#</span><span class="typ-pol">sym</span><span class="typ-punct">.</span><span class="typ-pol">checkmark</span><span class="typ-punct">]</span> for choosing one of the alternatives.


